me.taylorkelly.mywarp.warp.authorization

Class AuthorizationResolver

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.taylorkelly.mywarp.warp.authorization.AuthorizationResolver

  • public class AuthorizationResolver
extends java.lang.Object
    Resolves a user's authentication for a certain warp using a previously defined AuthorizationStrategy.

    There are three different non exclusive types of authorizations. A warp can be:

    1. modifiable,
    2. usable,
    3. viewable.
